snippet.title: Official Trailer | Online party game Astral Party is coming soon!
snippet.description:
Hi everyone!
We're happy to publicize #AstralParty 's trailer!


An online party game that focuses on rolling dice, triggering random events, leveling up, and winning!


🎲Will the dice goddess favor you?🎲


Add Astral Party to your wishlist!
